  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><p>Please download today&#39;s hiragana practice here: <a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/attachments/86e/725/dfa/Hiragana_Practice_Day_7.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Hiragana Practice Day 7.pdf</a></p><p>Practising writing hiragana every day is a very important exercise to help you learn quickly. If you have any questions you can always ask other students and teachers in the community <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p><p>To learn and practice the small tsu (っ) you can watch this free YouTube tutorial:<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hFbsWVMCgJM?t=233\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"></a><br><a href=\"https://youtu.be/hFbsWVMCgJM?t=233\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hFbsWVMCgJM?t=233</a></p></div>",
